						<div class="postbody">Thanks.<br /><br />So, if I want to make a game that will play on all devices, like old TVs, I need to not put anything important in the top or bottom 16 pixels, nor the side 8 pixels. Also, I noticed that old TVs displays are round at the corners - so, I might lose a few pixels in the corners too. Good to know for future games I work on.</div>

					
