					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Level 1 design completed, except for the enemies. I added a lot of features and fixed a lot of bugs. The only bug I still see, is...you can jump when your feet are a few pixels below a platform (you should only be able to jump if you're standing on a platform).<br /><br />Start - spawns 4 'enemies'<br />Select - shifts between tools that you already have, you have to hit enemies to get '?' to collect a tool.<br /><br />Feel free to give constructive criticism.<br /><br />(LINK REMOVED, OLD)<br /><br />Also, I know the ninja can jump way up into the HUD. I prefer that to having him disappear.<br />And, Level 1-7 is where the boss is supposed to appear, that's why scrolling stops.</div>

					
