						<div class="postbody">Here's the latest update of my new game. I added all the enemies for level 1, and fixed about a dozen bugs. There is still one unresolved bug, but it only happens about 1 out of 100 times and I came up with a crude fix for that.<br /><br />Still need to write the boss code, and rewrite the music. Not sure what I'm going to make the boss. It was going to be like a big guy with a sword or axe, but now I think that would clash with the cartoony nature of the other enemies. Hmm.<br /><br />(LINK REMOVED, OLD)<br /><br />Let me know if it's too easy / too hard / other problems. Thanks.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://nesdoug.com" class="postlink">nesdoug.com</a> -- blog/tutorial on programming for the NES</div>
					
