					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Another 'quirk' is that if you throw a tool and immediately press select, the tool disappears. That's because I added the select='switch tools' very late, and it caused the onscreen tools turn into other tools and behave wrong - because I define their movements and tiles by what tool you currently have selected. In retrospect, I should have defined them differently. My quick fix was to move them off screen on 'select' presses, but it looks stupid if done quickly. I may not fix this one either.</div>

					
